column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(sp.type) as type, sp.modelMag_u, sp.modelMagErr_u, sp.modelMag_g, sp.modelMagErr_g, sp.modelMag_r, sp.modelMagErr_r, sp.modelMag_i, sp.modelMagErr_i, sp.modelMag_z, sp.modelMagErr_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN SpecPhotoAll sp ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
